WEBVTT

00:03:57.447 --> 00:04:03.037
Kila mruko itafuta mbali kumbukumbu yeyote
ya historia ya ulimwengu ya nyuma.

00:04:03.037 --> 00:04:06.023
Matukio yapi kati ya haya
yatakuwa sahihi?

00:04:06.023 --> 00:04:09.253
Jibu linategemea na umbo halisi
la ulimwengu,

00:04:09.253 --> 00:04:11.543
kiasi cha nguvu ya gizai iliyobeba,

00:04:11.543 --> 00:04:14.133
na mabadiliko ya kusambaa kwake.

00:04:14.133 --> 00:04:18.953
Na kwa sasa, mitazamo yetu inapendekeza
kua tunaelekea kwenye Mgando Mkubwa.

00:04:18.953 --> 00:04:24.443
Japo habari njema ni kwamba tuna karibia
miaka 10 mpaka nguvu ya 100

00:04:24.443 --> 00:04:26.233
kabla ya ubaridi kuingia ---

00:04:26.233 --> 00:04:30.233
kwahiyo usianze kununua
kinga za mkononi bado.